{{Infobox ethnic group | group = Bangladeshis in Poland | population = 2500+ | popplace = [[Warsaw]] | langs = [[Polish language|Polish]]{{·}}various [[languages of Bangladesh]]{{·}}[[English language|English]] | rels = [[Islam]]{{·}}[[Hinduism]] }}
The '''Bangladeshi community in Poland''' consists of migrants from [[Bangladesh]] to [[Poland]] and their locally born descendants.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.en.sangbadprotikkhon.com/petta-festival-of-expatriate-bangladeshis-in-poland/|title=PETTA festival of expatriate Bangladeshis in Poland|work=Sangbadprotikkhon|access-date=2017-12-01|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bonappetour.com/sumona/street-foods-from-bangladesh|title=Street Foods from Bangladesh|website=BonAppetour|language=en|access-date=2017-12-01}}</ref> There are approximately 2,500+ Bangladeshis in Poland. In 1994 illegal migrants from Pakistan and Bangladesh arrived in Poland through Ukraine on the way to the west on a Soviet helicopter.<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6SKajP4vk3cC&pg=PA104&dq=Bangladeshis+in+Poland&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj2q5mK3-fXAhXjcd8KHcMZCAcQ6AEIJzAA#v=onepage&q=Bangladeshis%20in%20Poland&f=false|title=Trafficking in Migrants Through Poland: Multidisciplinary Research Into the Phenomenon of Transit Migration in the Candidate Member States of the EU, with a View to the Combat of Traffic in Persons|last=Siron|first=Nathalie|last2=Baeveghem|first2=Piet Van|date=1999|publisher=Maklu|year=|isbn=9789062156559|location=|pages=104|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mD-xCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA52&dq=Bangladeshis+in+Poland&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj2q5mK3-fXAhXjcd8KHcMZCAcQ6AEILTAB#v=onepage&q=Bangladeshis%20in%20Poland&f=false|title=The Challenge of East-West Migration for Poland|last=Sword|first=Keith|last2=Iglicka|first2=Krystyna|date=1999-02-12|publisher=Springer|year=|isbn=9781349270446|location=|pages=52|language=en}}</ref> Bangladesh has sent skilled migrants to Poland, including trade trainers.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theindependentbd.com/printversion/details/123508|title=Bangladeshi skilled labourers get job in Poland|last=Independent|first=The|work=Bangladeshi skilled labourers get job in Poland {{