The community of '''Britons in Egypt''' includes British migrants in [[Egypt]], as well as Egyptian citizens of British descent. In 2006, the Institute for Public Policy Research estimated that 14,000 British people were resident in Egypt.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/spl/hi/in_depth/brits_abroad/html/africa.stm|title=Africa|work=Brits Abroad|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=29 March 2018}}</ref>

